{"tid":1518432,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【請廣傳】各位手足 出發前請注意撒退（逃生）路線","createTime":"2019-08-30T08:56:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T09:34:08.000Z","uid":278414,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"40f83d1988cfa72c54fd076d60e2f61ad0a8c856","tid":1518432,"uid":278414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T08:56:34.000Z","msg":"昨晚SSP的圍捕直播後<br />\n代朋友出post<br />\n(p牌推唔到 麻煩幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/videos/458070588080853/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhk.nextmedia%2Fvideos%2F458070588080853%2F&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUivY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=b811ef8c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/videos/458070588080853/</a><br />\n（10:40開始）<br />\n<br />\n尋日appledaily LIVE見狗狗拉人地方是遠離大隊，<br />\n行好遠先見到狗狗大隊。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hsusueb/videos/748184708945380/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhsusueb%2Fvideos%2F748184708945380%2F&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUivY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=fbe746c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hsusueb/videos/748184708945380/</a><br />\n<br />\n差佬咩招都用，7人車已經好平常。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">尋日深水埗，掉完石5分鐘即有人被拉<br />\n應該係狗狗匿左示威者逃生路線，小路埋伏！</span></strong><br />\n(3個夠拉低你，街坊diu都救唔到)<br />\n<br />\n尋日appledaild LIVE見係離狗狗大隊好遠，<br />\n拉人既狗狗都係外圍離大隊好遠，<br />\n而唔係大隊狗狗拉人。<br />\n<br />\n真係唔想咁多有戰鬥力既手足俾人拉，<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">各位手足，出發前請計劃及注意撒退（逃生）路線</span></strong><br />\nBe water‼️"},{"pid":"befba2312ba2088c55fc0d0d2e2fb77281925acd","tid":1518432,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T08:57:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OUQvG7y.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOUQvG7y.gif&h=0b84475f&s={SIZE}\" /><br /